    "scale_info": {
      "name": "Long COVID - Current Quality of Life - Child",
      "code": "PX992301",
      "abbreviation": "PX992301",
      "description": "The Long COVID in Children and Young People (The CLoCk Study) “How you feel about your overall health” section contains 9 items prompting for a participant’s perception of their everyday life. Four items measure if a respondent has problems doing everyday tasks and the remaining five items measures ",
